title: China: consumers boost Q1 growth despite trade worries
text:
China: consumers boost Q1 growth despite trade worries 9:41am EDT - 01:37 
China's economy grew at a slightly faster-than-expected pace of 6.8 percent in the first quarter, buoyed by strong consumer demand, healthy exports and robust property investment. David Pollard
